1. On *pije* vodu. (He is drinking water.)
2. Ona *pije* kafu. (She is drinking coffee.)
3. Njegov otac *pio* je pivo. (His father was drinking beer.)
4. Oni *piju* sok. (They are drinking juice.)
5. Moj brat *pio* je ƒçaj. (My brother was drinking tea.)
6. Mi *pijemo* vino. (We are drinking wine.)
7. Da li vi *pijete* sok? (Are you drinking juice?)
8. Mi smo *pili* vodu. (We were drinking water.)